text: Þis synt þa landgemæro to ealdingtune.

Ærest on westan raculfinga mearce be þære ea norþ be raculfinga mearce on þone hrycg peg &lang weges oþ þone niwan dic andlang dices oþ mildryðe mearce suþ andlang merce on þa ea wantsume andlang wantsume oþ raculfinga mearce.
Þis is þara twelf sulunga boc æt Ealdingtune þe Eadmund cing gebocode Ælfstane his þegne on ece yrfe.
